<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-82-0835 </DOCNO><TEXT>Presents a control system for operational and managerial purposes in themining industry. Main part of this system is an indicator of the stateand conditions of individual machines and equipment (ready to start,in operation, defective, switched off, overloaded, idle work, etc.).Information provided by this indicator is numerically coded and presentedeither on a screen or on matrix cards. An analyzer and one counter areused to produce shift and daily reports as well as monthly reports onoutput, effective working time, idle working time of machinery and equipmentand to get an on-line picture of the production process, state of maintenance,reliability and availability of machinery, etc. 2 refs.</TEXT></DOC>